Lecture_1:
Problem thakle office hour e sir er shathe contact korte hobe.

Scheduling:
(state 3 dhoroner)
Basic Idea: Onek gula process ready state e thakle, tokhon kono ekta process k 
ene amra run korbo, kontake anbo, shei decission jei algorithm diye nei, shetai
holo shechuding algorithm.

Scheduler's goal: shobkichu efficiently use kora.

mainframe computer: onek boro calcultion er jonno jei computer used hoy, asholei
jara compute kore, shei computer gular resource onek scarce... no opochoy is 
feasible.

Process Behavior:
lifecycle of process: computing time + waiting for i/o(emon kaj jekhne cpu used
hocche na, shudhu i/o thaklei sheta ei khetre i/o na(cpu jokhon idle))

process er jibone:
1. CPU burst : jokhon computing e ase
2. waiting for i/o
ei 2 tar jekono ekta cholte thake

CPU burst long hole shei process k bole CPU bound process 
i/o waiting long hole shei process k bole i/o bound process

ekta process cpu bound naki i/o bound hobe sheta depend kore cpu burst er size 
er upor only. karon i/o waiting er time khubi kom hoy, kintu cpu burst shei 
tulonay onek boro hoy. 
shomoyer shathe shathe cpu burst er size kome jacche...
evabe komte komte ek shomoy shob process i/o bound hoye jabe

ekta prcess pura lifetime e 70% time idle thake. tahole cpu er utilization
maximize korte amader 12-14 tar moto process lage (see book).

i/o bound process k immediately run korte deya uchit. (why?)
karon process burst kom, ashar shathe shathe tar kaj shesh koray deya. then she
abar io te giye jate io device utilize korte pare.

When to Schedule:
